{
  "stem": "12447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, actually, it would-- the day would start, like, 6 o'clock that the curfew was over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it continued to the evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was kind of-- the day was pretty short because winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember, like, it was getting dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always tried to come back before, before the nightfall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't remember what time the curfew actually started in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How was it that you were able to get out without being seen in daylight?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- the wall was not watched by anybody because nobody expected anybody to crawl through that little hole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the hole must have been, I would say, maybe, like, I don't know, 20 inches by maybe 30 inches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, would be like 30 inches wide probably, maybe three foot wide, and maybe 15 to 20 inches high, just enough for the water to come through, but also enough for my head to go through and my shoulders.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once I was out, I did not have to come back through the same hole.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because coming back, you could come as a child to the gate, and they would let you in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the children that were out during the day were able to come back to the ghetto at that time without getting beaten up in the beginning or anything, as long as you did not try to go out.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Out was a problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would not let you out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In was much easier.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You came in through the gate, whatever you carried with you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you carried a disguise behind your coat or something, you were able to run into the ghetto without any problem.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
